{{no footnotes|date=February 2013}}
'''Amundsen Plain''' ({{Coord|65|0|S|125|0|W|display=inline,title}}) is an undersea [[abyssal plain]] named in association with [[Amundsen Coast]]. The name was approved by the [[Advisory Committee on Undersea Features]] in June 1988.

