'''Angel Falls''' is the second of two waterfalls on the Angel Falls Trail in [[Rabun County]], [[Georgia (U.S. state)|Georgia]]. The first waterfall on the trail is [[Panther Falls (Georgia)|Panther Falls]].<ref>[http://www.fs.usda.gov/wps/portal/fsinternet/!ut/p/c4/04_SB8K8xLLM9MSSzPy8xBz9CP0os3gDfxMDT8MwRydLA1cj72BTJw8jAwjQL8h2VAQAzHJMsQ!!/?ss=110803&navtype=BROWSEBYSUBJECT&cid=null&navid=110360000000000&pnavid=110000000000000&recid=10507&actid=70&ttype=recarea&pname=Chattahoochee-Oconee%2520National%2520Forest%2520-%2520Angel%2520Falls%2520Trailhead] USFS Website for Angel Falls</ref>
